The International Olympic Committee said athletes who qualified for the 2020 Games would retain their status for the postponed Games, in 2021.
Riley did not doubt that he belonged in the Tokyo Games, but then he started thinking about whether his status as an Olympian could help him pay for rent and food.
He started talking to his coach and manager about making sponsorship deals with shoe, watch and sunglasses companies.
